          <div class="mt-12 max-w-2xl">
              <h2 class="my-4 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">Next Steps</h2>
              <p class="my-4">
                  Hopefully this simple example shows how easy it is to get up &amp; running and become
